# Changelog

> N=new feature, E=error fix, F=fine-tune, R=refactor, I=infrastructure, T=tag

## Unreleased
- R Remove unused global hooks rebuildApp/refreshHome left from standalone Lists flow
- R Remove unused exitApp() leftover from standalone Lists home screen
- R Remove unnecessary underscores in lists photo errorBuilder (lint cleanup)

## 0.3.20260319+116
- E Unified backup/restore: fail the whole operation when lists.db backup/restore is missing or errors instead of reporting false success
- E Safer photo restore for memos/lists: use staging directories before replacing current photo storage
- E Lists photo migration: keep legacy source directories when migration is incomplete instead of deleting them unconditionally
- I 99-CopyToAPKX: use symlink instead of copy
- F Fix context.mounted → mounted in item dialog for consistency
- R Extract _removeFromDictionary() to deduplicate dictionary deletion logic

## 0.3.20260319+108
- F Unify dialog styles: shape, title font across all lists and shared dialogs
- F Replace hardcoded fontSize with fsSmall constant in item dialog
- F Add mounted checks after await in move items screen
